About Me I am a second year student in biology, and i study at the university of Mons, Belgium. I am 19 years old and i have been interested in biology since childhood. Before the beginning of my second year, i wasn't sure what i should do as a professionnal, and even if im still not really sure, i have been interested in toxicology and parasites subjects that we saw in Histology, physiology and bio animal.
